  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      public Project(String projectName, String neighborhood, Map<FlatType,FlatTypeDetails> flatTypes, Date applicationOpeningDate, Date applicationClosingDate, String managerNric, int maxOfficerSlots, List<String> approvedOfficerNrics, boolean visibility)
      Constructs a new Project object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      projectName - The name of the project. Must not be null or empty.
      neighborhood - The neighborhood of the project. Must not be null.
      flatTypes - A map of flat types and their details. Must not be null.
      applicationOpeningDate - The opening date for applications. Must not be null.
      applicationClosingDate - The closing date for applications. Must not be null and must be after opening date.
      managerNric - The NRIC of the managing HDB Manager. Must not be null.
      maxOfficerSlots - The maximum number of officer slots. Must be non-negative.
      approvedOfficerNrics - A list of approved officer NRICs. Can be null or empty.
      visibility - The visibility status of the project.
